column5:
#Newline 50#Newline#NewlineWelcome to my slot machine.
You start withcoins and each spin of the machine costs you 1 coin.
The game is over when you have either lost all your money or made 250 coins.
Good luck!

Type START to load the machine.

#Newline K K K pays 50
#Newline Q Q Q pays 25
#Newline J J J pays 15
#Newline 7 7 7 pays 7
#Newline A A - pays 2

#Newline You havecoins in the bank.

#Newline Type S to spin the reels
